description:
This version has reached End-of-Life (EOL) status and will no longer receive updates.

The unofficial Cats add-on for Blender 4.1 provides full compatibility and enhanced features for your avatar creation needs.

Known Incompatible Addons: Official Cats Blender Plugin and MMD Tools may cause conflicts as this version includes its own MMD Tools implementation.

Support is available through our Discord community, and comprehensive documentation can be found in our wiki.
